@startuml
!pragma teoz true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam DefaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"
skinparam DefaultFontSize 13
title 图26  统计报表生成顺序图

actor "票务管理员" as Admin
participant "管理端看板 (Vue 3)\nDashboard.vue" as FE
participant "AdminController\n/api/admin" as Ctrl
participant "AdminService" as AS
database "MySQL\nticket_order / ticket_item\nshow / show_schedule" as DB
participant "ECharts" as Chart
participant "DashboardRefreshPublisher\n/topic/admin/dashboard" as WS

Admin -> FE : 打开数据看板
FE -> Ctrl : GET /api/admin/dashboard
Ctrl -> AS : dashboard()
AS -> DB : selectList 订单/票据/演出/场次
DB --> AS : 实体集合
AS -> AS : 内存聚合(stream / groupingBy)\nKPI 卡片 + 近7日票房趋势\n+ Top5 热门演出 + 检票汇总
AS --> Ctrl : DashboardResponse
Ctrl --> FE : 200 OK + JSON
FE -> Chart : 渲染折线+柱状(双轴) / Top5 横向柱
Chart --> Admin : 展示数据看板
FE -> WS : SUBSCRIBE /topic/admin/dashboard

== 实时刷新 ==
WS ->> FE : DashboardRefreshEvent\n{reason: ORDER_PAID / TICKET_CHECKED_IN, ...}
FE -> Ctrl : 重新 GET /api/admin/dashboard
Ctrl --> FE : 最新数据 -> 局部更新

note over AS, DB
  聚合在应用层内存完成(非 GROUP BY SQL)；
  看板仅折线+柱状(无 Sankey/饼图/热力图)。
  下单/支付/检票触发 publish 推送刷新信号。
end note
@enduml
